args: *huff* *wheeze* Well, I'm deep in the\nwoods nyow. What a trial this has been!
But I managed to purr-ocure the eggs\nI needed, so all I have to do is get back\nto base and fry up some goodness!
Mrow! I knew something would show up!
I COULD leave the eggs and run for it...
But then I won't be able to make\na tasty dish for Vanessa!
There you are, kitty! Oh, I was so worried!\nAre you okay?! Are you hurt?!
I'm very glad you're all right, but why did\nyou run off and do something so reckless?
If something had happened to you, I'd...
'Cause I wanted to show you how I feel.
I was going to make you a special meal\nto apaw-logize for all the trouble I caused.
I went to the Hoary Woods to look for eggs,\nbut that ended up making even MORE\ntrouble! Oh, I'm a compurr-lete loser...
Look, you don't have to do anything\nspecial for me. I'll always... I mean...
Ugh! Fine. I'm gonna have to tell you\nhow I feel or else you'll never know.
Since I understand your feelings now,\nit's my turn to share mine.
After you left, all I could think about\nwas how to get along with someone\nwho isn't as strong as me.
But then I realized something:\nnone of that matters.
What DOES matter is getting to really\nknow the person you're thinking about.
So I sat down and tried super hard to\nthink about who you actually are, kitty.\nWanna hear what I came up with?
Well, to start with, you're SUPER adorable.\nIt makes my heart go pitty-pat whenever\nI look at you.
You're also kind, dependable with the cart,\nand dedicated. Oh, and a GREAT cook!

But most of all, you're just a good cat.
You went to a whole lot of trouble for me,
and there's no one else like you in this
or any other world!
That's why I care about you so much,\nand why I want you as my friend!
We're shaking hands. Hands and paws!\nKnow why it feels so warm? Because I'm\nhappy!
Because I know purr-lenty about\nwhat makes you great, which is why\nI want to be your friend!
And since you feel the same way,\nit makes me wanna purr all day!
Sorry for the wait, everybody, but the\nmain course is here in all its eggy glory!
We worked our tails off to make this,\nso make sure you eat lots!
Well, this smells a treat! Was it perhaps\nmade from eggs gathered from the giant\nbirds in the depths of the Hoary Woods?
Correctamundo! That's quite the\npurr-ceptive eye you've got there.
Well then, I shall savor the chance\nto enjoy the fruits of your friendship.
Oh boy, I've been waiting\nfor this all day. Let's dig in!
Hello, Vanessa. I'm pleased the two\nof you seem to have patched things up.
And it's thanks to you, so I want you\nto enjoy some of this chow!
I would be glad to share in your meal.\nWhat exactly are we celebrating, though?
Oh, I think it's pretty obvious...
We're celebrating the two of us\nbecoming best friends!
